quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  33,36,aur kisi momin mard aur momin aurat ko haq nahi hai ke jab khuda aur is ka rasool koi amar muqarrar kar dein to woh is kaam mein apna bhi kuch ikhtiyar samjhain. aur jo koi khuda aur is ke rasool ki nafarmani kere woh Sarih gumraah hogaya
  33,37,aur jab tum is shakhs se jis par khuda ne ahsaankiya aur tum ne bhi ahsaankiya ( yeh ) kehte they ke apni biwi ko apne paas rehne day aur khuda se dar aur tum apne dil mein woh baat posheeda karte they jis ko khuda zahir karne wala tha aur tum logon se drtay they. halaank khuda hi is ka ziyada mustahiq hai ke is se daro. phir jab Zaid ne is se ( koi ) haajat ( mutaliq ) nah rakhi ( yani is ko Talaq day di ) to hum ne tum se is ka nikah kardiya taakay mominoun ke liye un ke munh bolay biton ki biwion ( ke sath nikah karne ke baray ) mein jab woh un se apni haajat ( mutaliq ) nah rakhen ( yani Talaq day den ) kuch tangi nah rahay. aur khuda ka hukum waqay ho kar rehne wala tha
  33,38,paighambar par is kaam mein kuch tangi nahi jo khuda ne un ke liye muqarrar kardiya. aur jo log pehlay guzar chuke hain un mein bhi khuda ka yahi dastoor raha hai. aur khuda ka hukum ٹھیر chuka hai
  33,39,aur jo khuda ke pegham ( jon ke ton ) pohanchate aur is se drtay hain aur khuda ke siwa kisi se nahi drtay they. aur khuda hi hisaab karne ko kaafi hai
  33,40,Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam tumahray mardon mein se kisi ke waalid nahi hain balkay khuda ke paighambar aur nabiyo ( ki nabuwat ) ki mohar ( yani is ko khatam kardainay walay ) hain aur khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
  33,41,ae ahal imaan khuda ka bohat zikarkiya karo
  33,42,aur subah aur shaam is ki paki bayan karte raho
  33,43,wohi to hai jo tum par rehmat bhejta hai aur is ke farishtay bhi. taakay tum ko andheron se nikaal kar roshni ki taraf le jaye. aur khuda mominoun par meharban hai
